      <title>壳牌首席执行官谈第二季度收益、油价和股东回报</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-01/shell-ceo-on-earnings-oil-and-rewarding-shareholders-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[壳牌公司首席执行官 Wael Sawan 讨论了公司第二季度的业绩，因为收益超出预期，壳牌确认将再回购 35 亿美元股票。Sawan 还谈到了油价。“我们的资产负债表是长期以来最强劲的，”他说。他在《彭博社：开盘交易》节目中与 Anna Edwards 和 Tom Mackenzie 进行了交谈。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-01/shell-ceo-on-earnings-oil-and-rewarding-shareholders-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 10:35:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
